{"tid":1123303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新民調：韓國瑜45% 柯文哲31% 蔡英文19%  國民黨穩勝","createTime":"2019-04-24T11:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T17:43:26.000Z","uid":62257,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e425a1364c33a8a20dd4e0f79cf34cde35db6d47","tid":1123303,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E9%83%AD%E5%8F%B0%E9%8A%98%E7%B7%8A%E5%92%AC%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%BF%913-%E8%94%A1%E8%B3%B4-%E5%90%84%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%86%E5%A2%8A%E5%BA%95-143000802.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%258A%2598%25E7%25B7%258A%25E5%2592%25AC%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E8%25BF%25913-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%25B3%25B4-%25E5%2590%2584%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%259A%2586%25E5%25A2%258A%25E5%25BA%2595-143000802.html&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0hURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=7ddc4d07\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E9%83%AD%E5%8F%B0%E9%8A%98%E7%B7%8A%E5%92%AC%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%BF%913-%E8%94%A1%E8%B3%B4-%E5%90%84%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%86%E5%A2%8A%E5%BA%95-143000802.html</a><br />\n2019年4月23日 下午10:30<br />\n針對是否參選2020總統大選，高市長韓國瑜23日表態不參加現行制度初選，引起外界正反解讀；而據「時勢研究」晚間釋出最新大規模網路民調，在「藍白綠」7位人選中，韓國瑜以25.5%的支持度居冠、郭台銘則以22.8%居次，雙方僅差距2.7%。但若「排韓」以6人為選項，則以郭的36.3%居冠、台北市長柯文哲20.1%居次。<br />\n<br />\n而在「有韓／排韓」2種組合中，以「白色力量」為號召的柯文哲以17%及20.1%分居第3及第2名；至於現任總統蔡英文，分別以11.8%及11.7%的支持度位居第4、前行政院長賴清德則分別以9.6%及10.9%的支持度位居第5。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tUkK_75UwoUCH9nHbcTFLg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en-us/upmedia.mg.tw/6a14bf6d8c988e1804728f34603f1228\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtUkK_75UwoUCH9nHbcTFLg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-us%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2F6a14bf6d8c988e1804728f34603f1228&h=4b8eb48f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泛綠「英德之爭」 蔡英文領先賴7.2%<br />\n若以藍綠兩黨為政黨傾向劃分，泛綠民眾支持蔡英文達52%，賴清德支持度則是44.8%，雙方差距7.2個百分點。至於泛藍民眾方面，則以韓國瑜的39.7%居冠、郭台銘的37.6%居次、朱立倫以16.9%居第三、王金平則以4.2%墊底。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Udpv.3Dulvtwki0Jg6IW.Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en-us/upmedia.mg.tw/4e8e68be4581028bdda3d684e44be82c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUdpv.3Dulvtwki0Jg6IW.Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-us%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2F4e8e68be4581028bdda3d684e44be82c&h=0cd90298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020各參選組合民調 「郭韓」皆為勝選一軍<br />\n針對此次民調結果，時勢研究策略研究總監陳紀君博士指出，藍營的郭台銘及韓國瑜皆是一軍，以整體來說，無論何種決戰組合都有勝算，而若以國民黨4位候選人對比競爭，郭台銘則小勝韓國瑜；而民進黨「蔡賴」的支持度，則在藍綠白對決中敬陪末座<br />\n<br />\n在「韓柯蔡」的競選組合中，韓國瑜支持度達44.8%、柯文哲30.8%、蔡英文18.9%；而若只有「韓蔡」對決，韓國瑜則有高達59.8%的支持度，領先蔡英文的30.9%高達28.9個百分比。<br />\n<br />\n另在「郭柯蔡」的組合中，郭台銘以46.8%的支持度領先「柯蔡」，柯文哲及蔡英文分別以28.8%及17.5%落後；而若是「郭蔡」對決，郭台銘則以62%的支持度壓倒性領先蔡英文的28.7%，雙方差距高達33.3%。<br />\n<br />\n而若在以上2種組合中，將蔡英文替換為賴清德，對藍白營幾乎沒有影響。在「韓柯賴」組合中賴清德支持度為18.5%，落後給蔡英文的18.9%，但僅差0.04%；至於「郭柯賴」組合，賴清德以17.7%領先蔡英文的17.5%，差距僅0.02%。<br />\n<br />\n若朱立倫出戰「柯蔡」 朱38%微幅領先柯36.6%<br />\n另值得注意的是，在「朱柯蔡」組合中，朱立倫以38%支持度領先、柯文哲以36.6%居次、蔡英文則以18.4%落後，其中朱柯呈現拉鋸，雙方僅差1.4個百分比；而若為「朱蔡」對決，朱立倫則以56.8%領先蔡英文的31.9%。<br />\n<br />\n本次民調由「時勢研究」完成，以網路方式進行，依台灣選民結構的性別、年齡及地區分布為隨機樣本，執行日期為4月19日至22日間；男女比例為49.6%及50.4%；年齡分布20-29歲達19%、30-39歲達21%、40-49歲22%、50-59歲21%、60-69歲17%；調查地區涵蓋全台20縣市 ，最終蒐集1068份有效問卷結果；針對此次民調結果，時勢研究策略總監陳紀君也表示，網路調查不同於一般電話調查，具高教育程度、高回答率等特點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7QXHhXC86an1mE5enod08A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en-us/upmedia.mg.tw/9b9cd2fe0f1c1f36181dc158efd36780\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7QXHhXC86an1mE5enod08A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-us%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2F9b9cd2fe0f1c1f36181dc158efd36780&h=f3f2d86e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a52324020418c0b548de41ac14a707f9ebb951aa","tid":1123303,"uid":106591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"台灣發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d0fb8f13f5d267a22f5e3e0e1b8c21956e4b25","tid":1123303,"uid":145277,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"回歸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a609cd2d003dfbf6cc5de59c8137c52201acde5e","tid":1123303,"uid":62494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"至於泛藍民眾方面，則以韓國瑜的39.7%居冠、郭台銘的37.6%居次<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9,出韓贏面大過郭台銘好多wo,點解會有泛藍人支持郭"},{"pid":"7283b86e5e0446376efa90f5c88c587438bdce69","tid":1123303,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"美應考慮停售f16v俾台灣"},{"pid":"8298bbd45aac58c650425c9645ff311adfedc5c0","tid":1123303,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a609cd2d003dfbf6cc5de59c8137c52201acde5e","tid":1123303,"uid":62494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"至於泛藍民眾方面，則以韓國瑜的39.7%居冠、郭台銘的37.6%居次<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9,出韓贏面大過郭台銘好多wo,點解會有泛藍人支持郭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"2個都win"},{"pid":"dab683767cbeb1ef0b4133159694dabba577975d","tid":1123303,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306b1f00408da80184284666b2a7fd9607d1280d","tid":1123303,"uid":6623,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"有d想睇到台灣比大陸收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7aa9493ae4cc3e17a4a438ca6385bea648646f","tid":1123303,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"郭台銘係咪負責界韓國瑜啲票?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b2b512d0251e29f89da1d3f19ef4fd18dc51fc","tid":1123303,"uid":46500,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:32:27.000Z","msg":"下次總統選舉藍綠出選都一定分裂<br />\n<br />\n除非支那來緊哩一年繼續激嬲台灣人 蔡英文就可以打保護台灣哩張牌<br />\n<br />\n否則綠營2020真係凍過水<br />\n<br />\n藍營就更仆街 賣國瑜根本冇年輕人支持佢 哩D民調只有老中會做 冇曬代表性<br />\n<br />\n剩返果班邊個上都要比人話賣台<br />\n<br />\n無黨派嘅話又係慘 柯文哲就算選到都冇班底 政府入面大把人扯佢後腳<br />\n<br />\n綠營時代已經比藍營搞住 無黨派更加麻煩"},{"pid":"9ddfa62843125e83077d52d78e0c50474c68b49f","tid":1123303,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"306b1f00408da80184284666b2a7fd9607d1280d","tid":1123303,"uid":6623,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"有d想睇到台灣比大陸收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:32:27.000Z","msg":"蠢過豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9825d855adadb23711bd613752c47ef5dd5155","tid":1123303,"uid":52946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"好想睇台灣變成香港 咁到時中國就會放盡晒去同化香港 變成大陸一個3線城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bca95df1029c7de1d928b9cebbed247bdc4ce05","tid":1123303,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:32:47.000